# Unblock IPs Blocked by Cpanel csf

To unblock IPs taht are blocked by the cpanel/WHM csf follow these steps:

```
Login to your WHM panel i.e IP:2087
```

Then  goto "configserver security&firewall " as shown in label 1 in the figure below.


- Next click on the "Firewall Deny IPs" as in label 2


```diagram

```

2. Next We will be directed to another page with the list of blocked IPs.

Here we have to select the IPs to remove from the list and remove them. The reason why they were blocked will also be listed there.

See the figure below:


```diagram

```

3. Next click on change as shown in figure below:

```diagram

```

4. Next click on "Restart csf+lfd" as in figure below:

```diagram

```

Now you have removed the IP blocking from your server.
